{"tid":2136654,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"CCCU 改名UOWCHK與名牌大學結盟","createTime":"2020-08-02T10:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T06:27:30.000Z","uid":225931,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5906877875fe29f98294fccef49e39eb7124a3","tid":2136654,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbUpETy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbUpETy.jpg&h=40c36b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伍倫貢大學（UOW）是澳大利亞其中的頂尖學府之一，每年有近6,000名國際學生在其澳大利亞校園就讀。作為世界大學排名前2% 的名校，<span class=\"red\">UOW 致力與各行各業合作，以提供著重職業發展的學位課程，加上具備一流的配套設施，學校因此在國際上享譽盛名</span>。UOW 全面接管香港城市大學專上學院（CCCU），並將其更名為香港澳大利亞伍倫貢書院(UOWCHK)，成為UOW 全球高校網絡的一部份。<br />\n<br />\n集團行政總裁馬傲安（Marisa Mastroianni）指，香港的教育基礎設施令這裡成為 UOW 推出優質學術課程的理想地點，她表示：「香港擁有高水平且監管完善的教育體系，同時匯聚許多世界一流的機構，這些優勢為 UOW 提供了有力的支持，亦與我們擅於為旗下多個校區的學生提供優質課程的名聲相符合。 」她補充道：「在教育局與香港學術及職業資歷評審局致力確<br />\n保高等教育的水平下，香港在高等及專業教育監管方面擁有成熟健全的法律架構。 」此外，馬傲安認為香港是發展教育事業的理想地點，她表示：「在香港，優質教育受到高度重視，而從國際角度來看，香港相較其他地方而言，仍然是一個極具吸引力的著名留學地點。 」<br />\n<br />\n香港澳大利亞伍倫貢書院目前提供逾 30 個副學士學位課程，當中包括會計與金融、航空、創意媒體及設計、工程、資訊科技和心理學等學科。此外，書院還為學生提供相關的 UOW 銜接學士學位課程，務求達至相輔相成之效。<br />\n<br />\n學院將於今年9月開辦6個學士課程，包括會計學學士（榮譽）、日本研究（榮譽）文學士、中國語言文學及傳意（榮譽）文學士、營運及管理（榮譽）航空學士、金融學（榮譽）工商管理學士，以及社會創新（榮譽）社會科學學士）。<br />\n<br />\n學院指出，上述學士課程的報名費為150元，第一年及第二年學費分別為6.9萬元；第三及第四年則為7.4萬元；學院續指，課程將列入香港自資學士學位課程免入息審查資助計劃，於2019/20學年，合資格同學可獲資助3.13萬元。<br />\n<br />\n同時，為慶祝學院開辦課程，入讀首屆學士課程的學生，首年或第三年可獲香港伍倫貢學院學士課程創立基金分別提供1萬或1.5萬元額外資助。總計兩項資助，同學於首年所須繳付的學費可低至2.77萬元。"},{"pid":"76aae73493fadabd05096159a7d2618920de2895","tid":2136654,"uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">Start your journey Study at UOW</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZhiKna.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZhiKna.jpg&h=a2637b59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VDNCH5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VDNCH5.jpg&h=dcd822ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsEtm9L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsEtm9L.jpg&h=e3a0726d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2L7Om9L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2L7Om9L.jpg&h=c58900d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <a href=\"https://www.uow.edu.au/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uow.edu.au%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=ec0b8be2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uow.edu.au/</a>"},{"pid":"3329542cb10fe23bf83707b6ae4a576edfe08ee5","tid":2136654,"uid":117344,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:21:17.000Z","msg":"屌咪又係asshole仔"},{"pid":"0dc137bc960153e01c79bd0e9ccfcbc4eb0feb51","tid":2136654,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:32:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gKuKRM8zPoY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgKuKRM8zPoY&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=242ccccf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gKuKRM8zPoY</a><br />\n<strong>Enjoy surf camp in Australia</strong>"},{"pid":"4fdd7cfc8020175a4fa322f61030c46333996f51","tid":2136654,"uid":284432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6046f52da6348adab2b8b5ae8e11b681e1ba40d0","tid":2136654,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dc137bc960153e01c79bd0e9ccfcbc4eb0feb51","tid":2136654,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:32:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gKuKRM8zPoY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgKuKRM8zPoY&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=242ccccf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gKuKRM8zPoY</a><br />\n<strong>Enjoy surf camp in Australia</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:42:18.000Z","msg":"有得ocamp滑浪"},{"pid":"78cd849ef7ed06c7fe4a6ab64627bca8600293c2","tid":2136654,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cc2040b28226b9a82f0e40cb23311b8b754685","tid":2136654,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:28:56.000Z","msg":"名牌大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8448c80cd5bc3e1a88517dd4256e8a9f439c3f","tid":2136654,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a941f0b57c5b7e5433d120070dfeab9c1371faea","tid":2136654,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:30:16.000Z","msg":"老實講好過cityu"},{"pid":"85e4afa4dc5b96faeed2689879600586144188dc","tid":2136654,"uid":141895,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"City 班lecturer 同埋tutor 全部支那狗壟斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英文又廢又重口音聽到好辛苦<br />\nUOW 教書嗰班就真係真&middot;香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大部分都資歷老過city 嗰班同埋教得好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4367ab16617257cc8b694b01ecf289b59acca29c","tid":2136654,"uid":155684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"認真講，佢係Asso界既T0 院校"},{"pid":"94a4e06d3bc57612590069ca2079216985ef9676","tid":2136654,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102284e2e0937a67cf46707821847f40e5c5cee6","tid":2136654,"uid":112390,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\nnonju有自己嘅難處同彩數 <br />\n<br />\n如有得揀dse直入 邊個唔想<br />\n我都有努力過 我都試過每日訓4個鐘咁去溫書 操pp<br />\n咁我唔得即係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人鍾意男人 有人鍾意女人<br />\n各有取向<br />\n<br />\n有人適合DSE高壓模式一試定生死<br />\n有人適合HD/Asso持續考核GPA計分<br />\n各有自己選擇<br />\n<br />\n啲人覺得DSE考得差就一定係讀唔到書？一定唔應該入大學？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就真係勸啲人睇多啲書 唔好坐井觀天、活在自己嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n同埋nonju入hku唔令我覺得羞恥 亦唔係後門狗 nonju入hku係光明正大寫喺hku個website<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係啲人覺得只有DSE jupas先係光明正大入HKU嘅唯一選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lmao <br />\n<br />\nnonju都用自己努力考gpa 一步一步升上去 <br />\n（定係你覺得讀嘅hd/asso畀完錢就乜都唔洗理gpa自己就會好似啲警察受武肺感染人數咁自動升升升）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係畀錢 唔係靠關係 光明正大咁用非DSE嘅方式入HKU 我就真係唔知啲人憑乜嘢講nonju係走後門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實對比返我自己讀中學嘅經驗<br />\n讀完hd/asso嘅人 比起freshgrade嘅中學生<br />\n某程度上佢哋有更多嘅經驗喺接受全英嘅教學、寫paper &amp;reference （apa format）、group work合作、使用learn portal、應對freerider、睇百幾頁嘅ppt etc.（有錯望諒）<br />\n<br />\n大家雖然起點唔一樣 但最終都係為左讀大學 增長自己知識和技能 更好地融如社會 <br />\n未步入社會工作就已經要開始批鬥 分門別類 去區分前門後門 真係值得驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而至於hall收唔收我 唔到我話 <br />\n咁我禮拜一就打去admission office問下nonju嘅學生入唔入到hku 嘅hall<br />\n<br />\n而你用你認知嘅HKU hall文化覺得佢哋未必收我<br />\n<br />\n抑或可能係你坐井觀天呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後同宜家讀緊hd/asso嘅人講聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你來年過3爆4入到U"},{"pid":"d438b07ace867c36e0a8e834af751ab3da16cec0","tid":2136654,"uid":305553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:27:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}